summary: CONSUMER  CAN BE DRIVING DOWN THE HIGHWAY AND  VEHICLE CUTS  OFF WITHOUT WARNING.  CONSUMER HAS TAKEN IT TO THE SHOP 5 TIMES, AND THE MECHANIC COULD NOT FIND OUT WHY THE VEHICLE WAS DOING THIS.  AFTER IT CUTS OFF, IT TAKES AT LEAST 20 MINUTES TO A HALF AN HOUR TO GET IT STARTED AGAIN.    *AK
